//Congential heart disease - Ventricle septal defect (VSD)


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 of Cardio MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Congential heart disease' tab

When I select 'Ventricle septal defect (VSD)' from 'Congential heart disease' dropdown menu
Then 'Add pathology' button is enabled
And 'Membranous' radio button is enabled
And 'Outlet' radio button is enabled
And 'Inlet' radio button is enabled
And 'Trabecular' radio button is enabled

And 'Cardiomegaly' checkbox is enabled
And 'LA / LV increase' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dilated pulmonary artery' checkbox is enabled
